title: to join with gold
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2E3LPFP

by thenoblestroman

kintsugi is the japanese art of repairing broken pottery with lacquer dusted or mixed with powdered gold. it means, quite literally, ‘to join with gold.’ as a philosophy, it treats breakage and repair as part of the history of an object, rather than something to disguise.

jeongguk has fallen apart, is falling apart, and will fall apart far too many times than he can count. he returns home in hopes of being pieced back together again.

For me when I’m reading Fanfictions Hoseok is a Bottom. But I can also read Storys were he’s a Top.

I don’t really care so much about that.

But I have two things I don’t really like to read:

  1. Bottom Yoongi. With his personality he’s a Top. For me.
  2. Same goes to Namjoon

summary: Love Yourself: Answer has become the third BTS album and the third album overall to surpass 1 million sales on Hanteo and is now...
body:
Love Yourself: Answer has become the third BTS album and the third album overall to surpass 1 million sales on Hanteo and is now the best-selling Korean album of the 21st century. BTS is the only million-seller in Hanteo’s history.

BTS have also officially surpassed 10 million album sales on Gaon, making them the fastest act to achieve this feat.

BTS’ sales ALONE make BigHit the Korean entertainment company with the most album sales in 2018.
